headline: Expedia’s Fall Travel Outlook Provides Tips for Scoring the Best Prices During the Shoulder Season
summary: SEATTLE, August 21, 2025--Expedia®’s Fall Travel Outlook, released today, reveals key dates for budget-friendly travel this season. For domestic flights, the lowest fares can be found on September 29 and October 27. International travelers will find the best deals on October 26 and November 24.
